725
00:58:53,653 --> 00:58:55,319
Le di una sencilla...

726
00:58:56,439 --> 00:59:00,774
Hasta le escribí la maldi...

727
00:59:00,910 --> 00:59:03,160
Y ahora, mi...

728
00:59:03,279 --> 00:59:06,030
Mi maldita suerte.

729
00:59:06,115 --> 00:59:08,449
<i>...64, 65, 66...</i>

730
00:59:08,584 --> 00:59:09,950
Mierda.

731
00:59:10,086 --> 00:59:13,504
